Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:03.19,VampMain,Aka,0,0,0,,Trời xanh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.61,0:00:05.18,VampMain,Aka,0,0,0,,Biển xanh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.14,VampMain,Aka,0,0,0,,Cùng tận hưởng mùa hè nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:11.86,VampMain,Hin,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.42,VampMain,Aka,0,0,0,,Hinata-chan, lạnh quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:17.29,VampMain,Aka,0,0,0,,Đỡ nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:19.38,VampMain,Hin,0,0,0,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.69,VampMain,Hin,0,0,0,,Bắt được cậu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:24.08,VampMain,aka,0,0,0,,Đỡ nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:25.74,VampMain,hin,0,0,0,,Được!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.72,VampItalic,Sop,0,0,0,,Kiểu tra tấn gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:38.02,VampItalic,Sop,0,0,0,,Thế là ma cà rồng từ trắng thành trắng bệch...
